# Smart Attendance System Using Face Recognition

## Overview
AI-based attendance system using Python and OpenCV.

## Features
- Face Detection
- Face Recognition
- Automatic Attendance Marking
- Real-time Webcam Detection

## Technologies Used
- Python
- OpenCV
- Face Recognition
- NumPy
- Pandas

## How to Run
1. Install requirements
2. Add images inside images folder
3. Run attendance.py

